# Light Meter for Raspberry Pi

Source code for the Pi Light Meter can be found on [GitHub](https://github.com/andrew-rogers/DSP/tree/master/PiLightMeter).

The [PRBS dithered ADC](AwDocViewer.html?file=DSP%2Fhfn1bitADC.awdoc) is used for analogue to digital conversion in this application.

